      "id": "PopularPost45059",
      "post_content": "I seriously can't quite remember her being called the best card in Legions by many, given that this set also includes [Akroma, Angel of Wrath](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=42049) for instance.   \n  \nAlthough i agree that this is a pretty neat card.  \nHaving flash, this is an awesome response to board hosers.  \nAnd in general it's also a cheap choice to get two or more 2/2 bodies for just ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=G&type=symbol) after combat.  \nYet i'd preferably play her with an ensured use given by having something to get rid of your creatures.  \nPermanents that can sacrifice creatures like the aforementioned Nantuko Husk are useful.  \nEven better if they return another creature like [Apprentice Necromancer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Apprentice Necromancer), [Doomed Necromancer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doomed Necromancer) or [Hell's Caretaker](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hell's Caretaker).  \nIf you return another dead Caller of the Claw and produce further tokens.  \nTherefore [Second Sunrise](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Second Sunrise) might also be a good choice.  \n  \nBouncing it with [Wirewood Symbiote](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wirewood Symbiote) might also indeed b... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost45059\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">I seriously can't quite remember her being called the best card in Legions by many, given that this set also includes <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"42049\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=42049\">Akroma, Angel of Wrath</a> for instance. <br/><br/>Although i agree that this is a pretty neat card.<br/>Having flash, this is an awesome response to board hosers.<br/>And in general it's also a cheap choice to get two or more 2/2 bodies for just <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=G&amp;type=symbol\"/> after combat.<br/>Yet i'd preferably play her with an ensured use given by having something to get rid of your creatures.<br/>Permanents that can sacrifice creatures like the aforementioned Nantuko Husk are useful.<br/>Even better if they return another creature like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Apprentice Necromancer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Apprentice Necromancer\">Apprentice Necromancer</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Doomed Necromancer\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Doomed Necromancer\">Doomed Necromancer</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Hell's Caretaker\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Hell's Caretaker\">Hell's Caretaker</a>.<br/>If you return another dead Caller of the Claw and produce further tokens.<br/>Therefore <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Second Sunrise\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Second Sunrise\">Second Sunrise</a> might also be a good choice.<br/><br/>Bouncing it with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Wirewood Symbiote\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wirewood Symbiote\">Wirewood Symbiote</a> might also indeed b... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 45059)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '45059'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (1/10/2010 7:18:25 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRati