      "id": "PopularPost21380",
      "post_content": "Many consider her the best card in Legions and rightly so. There is nothing like your opponent's face after he plays  [wrath of god](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= wrath of god) or something only to end up staring down a whole mess of bears.  \n  \nShe also makes an insane combo with [nantuko husk](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=nantuko husk) and other sac creatures, especially when she goes back to your hand with [wirewood symbiote](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=wirewood symbiote).  \n  \n\\*Whoops, i meant to say the best *green* card in legions, my mistake.",
      "posted_by": "Laguz",
