      "id": "PopularPost54511",
      "post_content": "Yeah pretty neat card. Another good use for her is on the sideboard for a mono-green elf deck. This is an elf deck's best (and almost only) defense against board hosers (pyroclasm, wog, damnation, etc), which otherwise can set you back several turns or make you lose the game.",
